    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of a subdivision of the Tlingit Indian people in Alaska, on the coast between Cape Fox and Yakutat Bay, known for blankets and other cultural works.</Note_Text>
